{"tid":2210291,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"為什麼你不能讓自己太胖!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2020-09-20T09:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T07:18:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cb2b4b09d8c5e11d97f82765eeeeb3fad29f569e","tid":2210291,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"你需要理解的是<br />\n皮膚和肌肉是不同的彈性.<br />\n.<br />\n肌肉可以擴大<br />\n而且可以縮減<br />\n.<br />\n但皮膚可以伸展<br />\n但不能回頭<br />\n.<br />\n像一件襯衫一樣, 如果你穿到成隻香蕉咁<br />\n它將永遠不會恢復原樣.<br />\n.<br />\n所以不要讓自己<br />\n很胖, 因為即使你可以減肥.<br />\n並不意味著皮膚會恢復緊緊.<br />\n.<br />\n如果你不胖, 你仍然可以通過訓練來解決.<br />\n增加肌肉質量看上去滿了<br />\n.<br />\n但如果我太胖, 我就玩體重.<br />\n反正它會有一個香蕉部分.<br />\n.<br />\n注意吃東西.<br />\n亂食嘢可以很有趣, 好吃, 開心<br />\n.<br />\n但當我修理它時, 我累了<br />\n非常困難.<br />\n.<br />\n如照片所示, 只有手術去除皮革.<br />\n成本相當高.<br />\n.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HdSJNnx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHdSJNnx.jpg&h=fd71c340&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d28258c0e4a847a372406f3f51dd11a26dfd3cd5","tid":2210291,"uid":38904,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:59:56.000Z","msg":"粒lin頭好似黐上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cb341c6b8697aa89bd7031a4bb5ff4462872ae","tid":2210291,"uid":285681,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"師兄中文幾好 學左幾耐？"},{"pid":"513931995b36ab9b582fb138b5e05d835a3c854f","tid":2210291,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:04:30.000Z","msg":"咁係咪練太大隻都唔得"},{"pid":"d1a1b8b864ac6de1e0503c7c96d6f7dff9abf2fd","tid":2210291,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c9cb341c6b8697aa89bd7031a4bb5ff4462872ae","tid":2210291,"uid":285681,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"師兄中文幾好 學左幾耐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:04:34.000Z","msg":"google translate再改字，大部分唔係我打"}